---
title: Grilled Soy Chicken with Honey Fluffy Rice and Grilled Gai Lan
description: This Chinese-inspired dish will shake up your weeknight routine! Grilled soy-marinated chicken breasts are tossed in a sweet and sticky honey glaze, then sprinkled with crushed peanuts for a crunchy finish! Served with fluffy rice and grilled Gai Lan, you'll have this meal on the table in no time!
